               <msContents>
                  <summary><title type="supplied">An Icelandic Schwank
                        Collection</title><note>Contains around 200 short pieces of various
                        provenance: fairytales, legends, miracles, anecdotes and exempla often concerning
                        people from the Bible or world history. The stories are often provided with
                        short or no headings and never refer to a source. For a comprehensive list
                        of content, see <bibl><ref target="MarOve1979">Overgaard 1979</ref>,
                              <biblScope unit="page">274-282</biblScope></bibl>.</note></summary>
